# tf.io.read_file

Reads and outputs the entire contents of the input filename.

### Aliases:

* `tf.compat.v1.io.read_file`
* `tf.compat.v1.read_file`
* `tf.compat.v2.io.read_file`
* `tf.io.read_file`
* `tf.read_file`

``` python

    filename,
```
